Title: Babylon 5: Thirdspace
Writer: J. Michael Straczynski (creator), J. Michael Straczynski
Actors: Bruce Boxleitner, Claudia Christian, Mira Furlan, Richard Biggs
Plot: The crew of Babylon 5 discover a mysterious artifact of unknown origin. The artifact influences the minds of people aboard the station and endangers the lives of everyone aboard. Takes place during season 4 of the Babylon 5 TV series.
